data.content:
noun
the yellow pages
or the Yellow Pages
a phone book or part of a phone book that is printed on yellow paper, that lists the names, addresses, and phone numbers of businesses, organizations, etc., according to what they sell or provide, and that includes advertisements
In British English, Yellow Pages is a trademark. - compare white pages

Danh từ
danh bạ điện thoại giới thiệu các doanh nghiệp theo hoạt động của chúng, những trang vàng
